sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as System
    participant Channel as One-Way-Broadcast-Kanal

    User->>System: Request to create One-Way-Broadcast-Kanal
    System->>Channel: Initialize One-Way-Broadcast-Kanal
    Channel-->>System: Kanal created successfully
    System-->>User: Confirmation of Kanal creation
    User->>Channel: Send message
    Channel-->>User: Acknowledge message sent
    Channel-->>System: Broadcast message
    System-->>OtherUsers: Deliver message